cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper deals with the application of deep reinforcement learning techniques to incentivize the emergence of a grounded discrete communication protocol between general agents. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves natural language processing and communication, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of reinforcement learning techniques also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), while the focus on transfer learning suggests that it could belong to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
